UPDATE: i forget subscribe on beta ui extension developer program (details under the topic). Now, i can pick my extension in a tab, but the main component seens don't execute (the card is empty). Looking on network tab, i see one request to <http://localhost:8080/servers/ui-extensions-dev-server> that return 404 (print under topic) ... anyone have ideas?

-------------------------------------------------------------------

Hello all!

Im actualy trying to create a ui-extension (called open-finance-extension) following this documentation: <https://developers.HubSpot.com/docs/platform/ui-extensions-quickstart> , but actually, i can't continue because after i upload ( <https://developers.HubSpot.com/docs/platform/create-ui-extensions#add-the-card-to-the-record-view> ) the extension to HubSpot, she don't apear to me select inside contacts tab.

Any have any idea to fix it? (i trying to find others ideas on historic chat)

<#CCQ7H31D5|developer-tools> <#CLJJXGTC0|local-development>
After some hours, i found that i forget subscribe on beta for ui extensions explained here: <https://developers.HubSpot.com/docs/platform/crm-development-tools-overview#get-started>
